hadiths[46]{hadithnumber,text}:
449,"Hazrat Malik bin Sasaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik dafa main Baitullah key paas jaagney aur soney ki darmiyani keyfiyat mein tha ke teen aadmi aaye. eik aadmi un mein sey do key darmiyan tha. merey paas soney ka thal laya gaya jo hikmat aur eman sey bhara huwa tha. us darmiyan waley aadmi ney (mera badan) seeney sey ley kar pet key nichey tak chaak kar diya, phir us ney merey dil ko zamzam key pani sey dhoya, phir usey hikmat aur eman sey bhar diya gaya, phir merey paas khachchar sey chhota aur gadhey sey bada janwer laya gaya, phir main Jibril alehissalam key sath chala, chunanche hum pehley (qaribi) aasman tak aaye. (darwaza khatkhataaney par) puchha gaya : kon hai? Jibril alehissalam ney kaha : Jibril hun. puchha gaya : aur terey sath kon hai? (Jibril alehissalam ney) farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hain. kaha gaya : kya unhein bulaya gaya hai? (sawal aur jawab key baad darwaza khola gaya aur kaha gaya :) aap ko khush aamadeed ho. aap bahut hi khub aaye. (us aasman par) main Adam alehissalam key yahaan pahuncha aur mainey unhein salam kiya. unhoney farmaya : khush aamadeed ho tumhein aey merey betey aur Nabi ! phir hum doosrey aasman par aaye. puchha gaya : kon hai? kaha : Jibril, kaha gaya : aap key sath kon hai? kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) yahan bhi pehley aasman ki tarah huwa chunanche main Yahya aur Esa Alaihissalam key paas aaya aur mainey unhein salam kiya, unhoney kaha : khush aamadeed ho aap ko aey hamarey bhai aur Nabi ! phir hum teesrey aasman par aaye. puchha gaya kon hai? kaha : Jibril. kaha gaya : terey sath kon hai? kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wahan bhi isi tarah huwa chunanche main Yusuf alehissalam key paas aaya. mainey in ko salam kiya. wo kehney lagey : khush aamadeed ho aap ko aey bhai aur Nabi ! phir hum chauthey aasman tak pahunchey. wahan bhi wohi kuchh huwa. main Idrees alehissalam ko mila. mainey unhein salam kiya. unhoney kaha : khush aamadeed ho aap ko aey bhai aur Nabi ! phir hum paanchwen aasman par aaye. yahan bhi wohi kuchh huwa. main Harun alehissalam ko mila. mainey in ko salam kiya. unhoney kaha : khush aamadeed ho aap ko aey bhai aur Nabi ! phir hum chhatey aasman par pahunchey. wahan bhi yehi kuchh huwa. phir main Musa alehissalam key paas aaya aur mainey in ko salam kiya. unhoney kaha : khush aamadeed ho aap ko aey bhai aur Nabi ! jab main un sey aagey guzra to wo roney lagey. puchha gaya : aap kyon rotey hain? unhoney kaha : ya Rab ! ye nojawan jis ko tu ney merey baad Nabi banaya uski ummat sey meri ummat key muqabley mein ziyada log jannat mein jaeyngey aur wo afzal bhi hongey. phir hum saatwen aasman par gaey. wahan bhi yehi kuchh huwa. main Ibrahim alehissalam key paas gaya. in ko salam kiya. unhoney farmaya : khush aamadeed ho aap ko aey betey aur Nabi ! phir mujhey Baite-ma'moor dikhlaayaa gaya. mainey Jibril sey puchha to unhoney bataya ke ye Baite-ma'moor hai. is mein har roz sattar hazar farishtey namaz padhtey hain. jab wo us sey eik dafa nikal jatey hain to umr bhar dobara nahin aa saktey. phir mujhey Sidratul-muntahaa ki taraf buland kiya (chadhaya) gaya. uskey bair ilaaqa hijr key matkon key barabar aur uskey pattey haathi key kanon jitney badey they. uski jad mein chaar nehren thin. do poshida do zahir. mainey Jibril alehissalam sey puchha to unhoney bataya ke poshida nehren to jannat mein hain aur zahir neel aur faraat hain. phir mujh par pachas (50) namazein farz ki gaeen. main wapis Musa alehissalam key paas aaya to unhoney puchha : kya kar aaye? mainey kaha : mujh par pachas (50) namazein farz ki gaee hain. unhoney kaha : main logon ko aap sey ziyada janta hun. mujhey Bani-Israel ka zabardast tajarba hai. aap ki ummat hergiz is ki taqat na rakheygi lihaza wapis apney Rab taala key paas jaaeyn aur un sey takhfeef ka sawal karen. main dobara apney Rab taala key paas gaya aur takhfeef (kami) ka sawal kiya. Allah Taala ney in ko chaalis (40) bana diya. main phir Musa alehissalam key paas aaya to unhoney puchha : kya kar aaye? mainey kaha : Allah Taala ney chaalis (40) kar di hain. lekin unhoney phir pehli baat dohraai. main phir apney Rab taala key paas gaya to Allah Taala ney tees (30) kar den. main phir Musa alehissalam key paas gaya aur unhein bataya to unhoney phir pehli baat hi ki. main phir apney Rab taala key paas gaya to Allah Taala ney pehley bees (20) phir das (10) aur phir paanch (5) kar den. main phir Musa alehissalam key paas aaya to unhoney phir pehli baat dohraai. mainey kaha : Ab to mujhey apney Rab taala ki taraf jatey huye sharam aati hai. chunanche itney mein aelan huwa : mainey apna fariza jari (nafiz) kar diya aur apney bandon sey takhfeef (kami) ki aur main har neki ka badla das gona dunga."
450,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne Hazam (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney meri ummat par pachas namazein farz kin. main ye (hukm) ley kar lota yahan tak ke Musa alehissalam key paas sey guzar raha tha to unhoney kaha : aap ki ummat par Allah Taala ney kya farz kiya hai? mainey kaha : pachas (50) namazein farz ki hain. Musa alehissalam ney mujh sey kaha : aap apney Rab key paas jaeyn (aur takhfeef (kami) ka sawal karen) kyonkey aap ki ummat is ki taqat nahin rakhti chunanche main apney Rab ki bargah mein hazir huwa (aur takhfeef (kami) ka sawal kiya) to Allah Taala ney us ka eik hissa maaf farma diya. main phir Musa alehissalam ki taraf lota aur unhein bataya to unhoney kaha : phir Allah Taala sey ruju kijiye aap ki ummat is ki bhi taqat nahin rakhti chunanche main phir apney Rab taala ki bargah mein hazir huwa to merey Rab taala ney farmaya : namazein paanch hain magar sawab mein pachas hi hongi. baat merey yahaan tabdeel nahin hoti. main phir Musa alehissalam ki taraf lota to wo kehney lagey : phir Rab taala sey ruju kijiye. mainey kaha : tehqiq (ab to) mujhey apney Rab sey (baar baar takraar par) sharam aaney lagi hai."
451,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey paas eik janwer laya gaya jo gadhey sey bada aur khachchar sey chhota tha. us ka qadam wahan padta tha jahan uski nazar pahunchti thi. main Jibril alehissalam key sath is par sawar ho gaya. main kuchh chala to Jibril alehissalam ney kaha : utro ! namaz padho ! mainey namaz padhi. kehney lagey : aap jantey hain, kahan namaz padhi hai? aap ney Madina Tayiba mein namaz padhi hai aur usi ki taraf aap hijrat farmaeyngey, phir kehney lagey : utro ! namaz padho. mainey padhi. kehney lagey : aap jantey hain, kahan namaz padhi hai? aap ney Toore-seena mein namaz padhi hai jahan Allah Taala ney Musa alehissalam sey kalam kiya tha. phir kehney lagey : utro ! namaz padho ! main utra aur namaz padhi. kehney lagey : aap jantey hain, kahan namaz padhi hai? aap ney Baitul-laham mein namaz padhi hai jahan Hazrat Esa alehissalam paida huye. phir main Baitul-maqdis mein dakhil huwa. wahan merey liye Anbiya Alaihissalam jama kiye gaey they, chunanche mujhey Jibril alehissalam ney aagey kar diya. mainey un ki Imaamat ki. phir mujhey ley kar qaribi (pehley) aasman ki taraf chadhey. is mein Adam alehissalam they, phir wo mujhey doosrey aasman ki taraf ley chadhey. is mein do khaala-zaad bhai Esa aur Yahya Alaihissalam they, phir wo mujhey teesrey aasman ki taraf ley kar chadhey to is mein Yusuf alehissalam they, phir wo mujhey chauthey aasman ki taraf ley kar chadhey to is mein Harun alehissalam they, phir wo mujhey paanchwen aasman ki taraf ley kar chadhey to is mein Idrees alehissalam they, phir wo mujhey chhatey aasman ki taraf ley kar chadhey to is mein Musa alehissalam they, phir wo mujhey saatwen aasman ki taraf ley kar chadhey to wahan Ibrahim alehissalam they. phir wo mujhey saatwen aasman sey ooper ley gaey to hum Sidratul-mantahaa tak pahunchey. wahan mujhey eik badal ney dhanp liya. main sajdey mein gir pada. mujhey kaha gaya : tehqiq mainey jis din aasman aur zamin paida kiye they aap aur aap ki ummat par pachas (50) namazein farz kar di thin, lihaza aap aur aap ki ummat ye namazein padhein main Ibrahim alehissalam ki taraf lota to unhoney mujh sey kuchh nahin puchha phir main Musa alehissalam key paas aaya to unhoney kaha : Allah Taala ney aap par aur aap ki ummat par kitni namazein farz ki hain? mainey kaha : pachas. unhoney kaha : tehqiq aap itni namazein padh saktey hain na aap ki ummat is liye Rab taala key paas jaaeyn aur kami ka sawal karen. main apney Rab taala key paas gaya (aur kami ka sawal kiya) to Allah Taala ney das namazein kam kar den. main phir Musa alehissalam key paas aaya to unhoney dobara janey ko kaha. main phir gaya to Allah Taala ney mazeed das kam kar den. main phir Musa alehissalam key paas aaya to unhoney phir wapis janey ko kaha. main phir gaya to Allah Taala ney mazeed das kam kar den. aakhir-kar paanch reh gaeen. Musa alehissalam ney kaha : phir apney Rab key paas jaeyn aur mazeed kami ka sawal karen. tehqiq Bani-Israel par do namazein farz thin, wo do bhi na padh sakey. main phir Rab taala key paas gaya aur mazeed kami ki darkhaast ki. Allah Taala ney farmaya : mainey jis din zamin aur aasman paida kiye they, aap par aur aap ki ummat par pachas namazein farz ki thin. ab pachas ki bajaey paanch hain. so aap aur aap ki ummat inhein padha karen. mainey samajh liya ke ye Allah Taala ki taraf sey qataee hain. chunanche main Musa alehissalam key paas gaya to unhoney kaha : dobara jaeyn lekin mujhey ilm tha ke ye Allah Taala ki taraf sey qatae hain, lihaza main wapis na lota."
452,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Meraj karwai gaee to aap ko sidratul-muntaha tak ley jaya gaya. aur wo (us ki jad ) chatey aasman mein hai. nichey sey jo chiz ooper jati hai wo wahan ja kar ruk jati hai. aur ooper sey jo kuch utarta hai wo bhi wahan aa kar ruk jata hai, yahan tak ke wahan sey wasul kar liya jata hai. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ( اذ یغشی السدرۃ ما یغشی ) (Najm 53 : 16) sey murad soney key patingey hain ( jinhoney sidratul-muntaha ko dhanp rakha tha. ) wahan aap ko teen cheezen ata farmaai gaeen : paanch namazein, Sura Baqra ki aakhiri aayaat aur aap ki ummat key har us shakhs key kabayer maaf kar diye jaeyngey jo is haal mein faut huwa ke Allah key sath kisi chiz ko shareek na thehrata tha."
453,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke namazein Makka ( makki daur ) main farz huin. do farishtey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur aap ko zamzam ki taraf ley gaey, phir aap ka ( Sina aur ) pet cheera aur andruni cheezen soney key eik thal mein nikalin, phir in ko zamzam key pani sey dhoya, phir aap key pet mein hikmat aur ilm dal kar ooper sey band kar diya."
454,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke shuru shuru mein namaz do rakat farz hui thi, phir safar ki namaz isi tarah rehney di gaee aur hazar ( iqaamat ) ki namaz ( chaar rakat ) mukammal kar di gaee."
455,"Hazrat Auzai ney Hazrat Zohri sey puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina hijrat farmaney sey qabl Makka mein kaisey namaz padhtey they? unhoney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Urwa ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey bayan kya, unhoney farmaya : shuru mein Allah Taala ney apney Nabi par do do rakatein namaz farz ki thi, phir ghar ki namaz ko chaar rakat mukammal kar diya gaya aur safar ki namaz pehli haalat par rehney di gaee."
456,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke shuru mein namaz do do rakatein farz hui thi, phir safar ki namaz to itni hi rehney di gaee aur hazar ki namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya."
457,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani hazar ki namaz char rakat, safar ki namaz do rakat aur khof ki namaz eik rakat farz ki gaee."
458,Umayya bin Abdullah bin Khalid bin Usaid ney Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha ke aap namaz kaisey qasr kartey hain? jab ke Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : ( فلیس علیکم جناح . ۔ . un خفتم ) tum par koi harj nahin ke tum namaz qasr kar lo agar tumhein khof ho. Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya : aey merey bhatijey ! Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to hum gumrah they. aap ney hamen taalim di. jo kuch aap ney sikhaya is mein ye bhi tha ke Allah Taala ney hamen hukm diya hai ke hum safar mein do rakatein padhein ( Muhammad bin Abdullah ) Shaesi ney kaha : Zohri ye hadees Abdullah bin abu-Bakar sey bayan kartey they.
459,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Najad walon mein sey eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. uskey sar key baal bikhrey huye they. hum uski aawaz ki bhinbhinahat to suntey they lekin hamein uski baat samajh mein nahin aa rahi thi yahan tak ke wo qarib aa gaya to nagahani wo Islam key barey mein poochhney laga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : din aur raat mein paanch namazein hain. us ney kaha : kya inkey ilawa bhi koi namaz mujh par farz hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin, magar ye ke to nafl padhey. aap ney farmaya : aur maahe Ramzan key rozey hain. us ney kaha : kya unkey ilawa bhi koi roza mujh par farz hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin, magar ye ke to nafl rozey rakhey. isi tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey liye Zakat ka zikr farmaya. us ney kaha : kya uskey ilawa bhi mujh par kuchh (maali sadqa) farz hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin, magar ye ke to nafli sadqa dey. wo aadmi wapis muda aur keh raha tha : Allah ki qism ! na is sey zayed karunga na is mein kami karunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye sachcha huwa to kamiyab raha."
460,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala ney apney bandon par kitni namazein farz ki hain? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney apney bandon par paanch namazein farz farmaee hain. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya un sey pehley ya baad bhi kuchh farz kya hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney apney bandon par paanch namazein (hi) farz ki hain. to us aadmi ney qism khai ke wo is sey zayed padheyga na in mein kami kereyga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye sachcha raha to zarur jannat mein dakhil hoga.
461,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas (bethey) they ke aap ney farmaya : kya tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat nahin kartey ? aap ney ye jumla teen dafa dohraya to hamney apney haath aagey badhaey aur aap sey baiat ki, phir hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamney aap ki baiat to kar li hai magar ye kis baat par hai? aap ney farmaya : is baat par ke tum Allah Taala ki ibadat karogey aur uskey sath kisi ko shareek nahin thehraogey aur paanch namazein padhogey. aur aap ney eik baat aahista kahi : tum kisi sey kuchh nahin maangogey."
462,"Ibne Maheereez sey riwayat hai ke Banu Kinaana key eik aadmi ney jisey Makhdaji kaha jata tha, Sham key ilaqey main eik aadmi ko jiski kunniyat Abu-Muhammad thi, ye kehtey huye suna ke witr wajib hai. Makhdaji ney kaha : main Hazrat Ubaada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya jab ke wo masjid ko ja rahey they. mainey in ko aagey sey rok liya aur Abu-Muhammad key qol ki khabar di. Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : Abu-Muhammad ney ghalat kaha hai. mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna hai : paanch namazein hain jo Allah Taala ney bandon par farz ki hain, jo aadmi unhein ada karey. un mein sey kisi ko un ki haisiyat halki samajh kar zaya na karey to Allah Taala key yahaan uskey liye wada ho chuka hai ke wo usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga. aur jo shakhs in ko ada na karey to Allah Taala key yahaan uskey liye koi ehad nahin. chahey usey azab dey, chahey jannat mein dakhil kerey."
463,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : batao! agar tum mein sey kisi key darwazey key samney sey nehar guzarti ho, wo us sey har roz paanch dafa ghusl karta ho, kya us ka kuch bhi mail kuchail baqi reh jaeyga? Sahaba ney kaha : kuch bhi mail kuchail nahin rahega. aap ney farmaya : paanch namazon ki misal bhi yehi hai. Allah Taala unkey sath ghaltiyan mita deta hai."
464,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamarey aur un ( kafiron ) key darmiyan imtiyaaz namaz sey hai. jisney usey chhod diya us ney kufr kya."
465,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bandey aur kufr key darmiyan sirf namaz chhodney ka farq hai."
466,"Hazrat Hurriyat bin Qabeesa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke main Madina aaya to mainey dua ki : aey Allah ! mujhey koi nek hum nasheen muyassar farma. phir Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hum nasheeni muyassar hui. mainey un sey kaha : mainey Allah Taala sey dua ki thi ke mujhey nek hum-nasheen muyassar farma, lihaza aap mujhey koi aisi hadees bayan farmaain jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni ho. ummid hai Allah Taala mujhey us sey faeyda pahunchaeyga. aap ney bayan kiya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : sab sey pehley bandey sey namaz ka hisab liya jaeyga. agar wo durust hui to wo kamiyab aur kaamraan ho gaya. aur agar wo kharab hui to wo nakam raha aur khasarey mein gaya. Hamaam kehtey hain : mujhey malum nahin ke ye alfaz Qatada key hain ya riwayat (hadees) key hain. agar uskey farzon mein kuchh kami hui to Allah Taala farmaeyga : (aey farishto !) dekho kya merey bandey key paas kuchh nafl hain? to unkey sath uskey farzon ki kami puri ki jaeygi. phir baqi aamaal mein bhi isi tarah (hisab) hoga. Hazrat Abu Aawaam ney sanad mein Hazrat Hamaam ki mukhalifat ki hai."
467,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq qiyamat key din sab sey pehley bandey sey jis chiz ka hisab hoga wo uski namaz hogi. agar wo mukammal pai gaee to mukammal likhi jaeygi aur agar is mein kuch kami hui to Allah Taala farmaeyga : dekho ! kya tum uskey liye kuch nafl paatey ho jiskey sath uskey zaya karda farz ki kami puri kar di jaey. phir baqi aamal bhi usi key mutabiq jari hongey."
468,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey pehley bandey sey uski namaz ka hisab liya jaeyga. agar us ney namazon ko mukammal kya hoga (to durust) warna Allah Taala (farishton sey) farmaeyga : dekho! kya merey bandey key nama aamal mein koi nafl hain? agar nafl paey gaey to Allah Taala farmaeyga, un sey farzon ki kami ko pura kar do."
469,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey kisi aisey kaam sey muttala farmaain jo mujhey jannat mein dakhil kar dey. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum Allah Taala ki ibadat karo aur kisi ko us ka shareek na banao aur namaz sahih sahih ada karo, Zakat ada karo aur rishton ko jodo ( phir aap ney us aadmi sey kaha ) us ( oontni ki mahar) ko chhod do. goya ke aap oontni par sawar they."
470,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Zohar ki namaz Madina Munawra mein chaar rakat padhi aur Asr ki namaz Zul-Hulefa mein do rakat padhi.
471,"Hazrat abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) dophare key waqt . ۔ . ibne-Musanna ney kaha : Bat-ha ( Makka mein maqbara Maalaat sey Safa Marwa ki taraf janey waley raastey) ki taraf . ۔ . nikley. aap ney wuzu farmaya, phir Zohar o Asr do do rakat padhein aur aap key aagey eik chhota neza gaada gaya tha."
472,"Hazrat Ammara bin Rubiya Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : wo aadmi hergiz aag mein dakhil na hoga jisney Suraj tulu aur ghurub honey sey qabl ki namazein (Fajr aur Asr) ada kin."
473,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key azad karda ghulam abu-Yunus kehtey hain ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney mujhey hukm diya ke main unkey liye Quran Majeed ka eik nuskha likhun. farmaney lagen : jab to is aayat par pahunchey حافظوا Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلوت والصلوۃ الوسطی (Baqara : 238) namazon ki, khususan « صلاۃ وسطیٰ » ki pabandi karo. to mujhey ittila karna. jab main us aayat par pahuncha to aap ney mujhey yun likhwaya : حافظوا Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلوات والصلاۃ الوسطی وصلاۃ العصر وقوموا للہ قانتین phir farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey yunhi suna hai."
474,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( kafiron ney ) hamen صلاۃ وسطیٰ sey masroof rakha yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya."
475,abu-Mulaih bayan kartey hain ke hum eik abr-aalood din mein Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) key sath they to unhoney kaha : namaz ( Asr ) jaldi padh lo kyonkey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jisney Asr ki namaz chhod di us ka amal zaya ho gaya.
476,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Zohar aur Asr ki namaz mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qiyam ka andaza lagatey they. hamney Zohar ki namaz mein aap key qiyam ka andaza pehli do rakaaton mein sura sajda key barabar taqriban tees (30) aayaat lagaya aur aakhiri do rakaton mein us sey nisf. aur Asr ki pehli do rakaaton mein Zohar ki aakhiri do rakaaton key barabar aur Asr ki aakhiri do rakaaton mein us sey nisf qiyam ka andaza lagaya.
477,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki namaz mein qiyam farmatey to har rakat mein taqriban tees aayaat tilawat farmatey phir Asr ki pehli do rakaaton mein pandarah aayaat key b-qadr qirat farmatey.
478,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz Madina Munawra mein chaar rakat aur Asr ki namaz Zul-Hulefa mein do rakat padhi.
479,"Hazrat Naufal bin Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : jiski Asr ki namaz reh gaee, wo yun samjhey ke us sey uskey ehal o maal loot liye gaey. Irak kehtey hain : mujhey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney khabar di ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : jissey Asr ki namaz reh gaee, wo yun samjhey ke us sey uskey ehal o maal loot liye gaey. Yazid bin abi Habib ney (sanad aur matn key bayan mein Jafar bin Rabeea ki) mukhalifat ki hai."
480,"Hazrat Naufal bin Muawiya Raziallahu anhu ney bayan kya, mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : namazon mein sey eik namaz aisi hai ke jis sey wo reh jaey, wo yun samjhey ke uskey ehal o maal loot liye gaey. Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna ke wo Asr ki namaz hai. Muhammad bin Is-haq ney (Hazrat Les ki) mukhalifat ki hai."
481,Irak bin Malik ney kaha ke mainey Naufal bin Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna : eik namaz aisi hai ke jis sey wo reh jaey goya uskey ehal o maal loot liye gaey. Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo Asr ki namaz hai.
482,"Salma bin Kuheil sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Saeed bin Juber ko muzdalfa mein dekha, unhoney iqamat kahi aur maghrib ki namaz teen rakat padhi, phir iqaamat kahi aur Isha ki namaz do rakat padhi, phir unhoney zikr kya ke Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney us jagah in ko aisey hi namazein padhaein aur Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney zikr kya ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us jagah isi tarah kya tha."
483,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik raat) Isha ki namaz ko muakhkhar kya yahan tak ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap ko (masjid sey) buland aawaz mein pukara ke aurten aur bachey so gaey. to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bahar ( masjid mein) tashrif laye aur farmaya : tumharey ilawa koi shakhs ye namaz nahin padhta, aur (waqai) un dino ehale-Madina key ilawa koi shakhs namaz nahin padhta tha."
484,"Hazrat Hakam sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : janab Saeed bin Juber ney hamen muzdalfa mein maghrib ki namaz iqamat key sath teen rakat padhai, phir salam phera, phir Isha ki namaz do rakatein padhaain aur kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney aisey kya. aur unhon (ibne-Umar) ney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey hi kya tha."
485,"Janab Saeed bin Juber ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha, aap ney muzdalfa mein iqaamat kahi aur maghrib ki namaz teen rakat padhi, phir Isha ki namaz do rakat padhi, phir farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko us jagah isi tarah kartey dekha hai."
486,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat aur din key waqt farishtey tum par baari baari aatey hain aur Fajr aur Asr ki namaz mein (din aur raat key) farishtey jama ho jatey hain. phir jin farishton ney tum mein raat guzari hoti hai wo ooper jatey hain. Allah Taala un sey poochhtey hai, halanke Allah Taala apney bandon ko khub janta hai : tum merey bandon ko kis haal mein chhod kar aaye ho? wo kehtey hain : hum in ko namaz padhta chhod kar aaye hain aur jab hum unkey paas gaey they to wo us waqt bhi namaz padh rahey they."
487,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ba-jamaat namaz tumharey akeley ki namaz sey pachchees guna fazilat rakhti hai. aur Fajr ki namaz mein raat aur din key farishtey ikhattey ho jatey hain. chaho to Quran Majeed ki ye aayat padh lo (وقران الفجر ان قران الفجر کان مشھودا),""aur subah ki namaz qaaim karo kyonkey subah ki namaz mein farishtey hazir hotey hain.''"
488,Hazrat Ammara bin Rubiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : wo shakhs aag mein nahin jaeyga jisney tulu shams aur ghurub shams sey pehley ki namazein padhin.
489,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Baitul-Maqdis ki taraf ( munh kar key) sola (16) ya satrah (17) mahiney namaz padhi, phir aap ko mojud qibley ( baitullah ) ki taraf pher diya gaya."
490,"Hazrat Baraa bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra tashrif laye to aap ney saula (16) mahinon tak Baitul-maqdis ki taraf (munh kar key) namaz padhi, phir aap ka rukh Kaba ki taraf kar diya gaya. eik aadmi jisney (qibley ki tabdili key baad) aap key sath namaz padhi thi, Ansaar key eik qabiley key paas sey guzra to usney kaha : main qism khata hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka qibla Kaabey ki taraf kar diya gaya hai. to wo (namaz hi mein) Kaabey ki taraf mud gaey."
491,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni sawari par nafl namaz padhtey they, sawari ka munh jis taraf bhi hota. isi tarah witr bhi sawari par padhtey they. magar farz namaz sawari par nahin padhtey they."
492,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka sey Madina aatey huye sawari par namaz padhtey they aur usi key barey mein ye aayat utri : فاینما تولوا فثم وجہ اللہ tum jidhar bhi munh karo udhar hi Allah Taala ka chehra hai."
493,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) safar mein apni sawari par ( nafl ) namaz padha kartey they, jidhar bhi us ka munh hota. ( Hadees key raawi ) Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Abdullah bin Dinar ney kaha : ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bhi aisey hi kya kartey they."
494,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : log qubaa mein subh ki namaz mein they ke eik aaney waley shakhs ney kaha ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par aaj raat naya hukm utra hai aur aap ko kaabey ki taraf munh karney ka hukm diya gaya hai, lihaza kaabey ki taraf munh karo. unkey chehrey Sham ki taraf they, chunanche wo kaabey ki taraf ghoom gaey."
